{"tid":1408130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天航：一個人，一件小事，可以成就歷史！","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:03:08.000Z","uid":209097,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f72126c45ae2f67fb64ef16754b3718e8d0f542b","tid":1408130,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"此刻已經是八月五日，也許今天就是香港命運的轉捩點。<br />\n雖然我出來呼籲【罷工】是毫無說服力的，感覺就像給自己一個DELAY的借口（坦白說，我真的很喜歡罷工）。。<br />\n只希望我的呼籲能給猶豫中的朋友一點勇氣。<br />\n希望大家相信【罷工】是有用的，只要人數夠多，就能向政府施壓，政府就不得不對民意低頭。亦只有人數夠多，我們才能保護罷工的人。<br />\n明天就是民意的戰鬥，間接就是公投。<br />\n這也是最低成本的抗爭，如果香港人連這樣的小事也不敢做，政府一定更加為所欲為。<br />\n<br />\n一個人，一件小事，可以成就歷史！<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港！香港人可以團結！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/152506018099285/posts/2943422019007657?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F152506018099285%2Fposts%2F2943422019007657%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=225645bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/152506018099285/posts/2943422019007657?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"068c132818d01c21bbe5ab8b0960ecfc1d10bb8a","tid":1408130,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"ca37eab3075648cef6c105d2007153cd057bc7e5","tid":1408130,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068c132818d01c21bbe5ab8b0960ecfc1d10bb8a","tid":1408130,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"f3330605358a241c58c5a67ae329d4aa05d4872b","tid":1408130,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca37eab3075648cef6c105d2007153cd057bc7e5","tid":1408130,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068c132818d01c21bbe5ab8b0960ecfc1d10bb8a","tid":1408130,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:37:56.000Z",